org.apache.lucene.search

Class BlendedTermQuery.DisjunctionMaxRewrite

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.lucene.search.BlendedTermQuery.RewriteMethod
      • org.apache.lucene.search.BlendedTermQuery.DisjunctionMaxRewrite
  • Enclosing class:
    BlendedTermQuery

    public static class BlendedTermQuery.DisjunctionMaxRewrite
extends BlendedTermQuery.RewriteMethod
    A BlendedTermQuery.RewriteMethod that creates a DisjunctionMaxQuery out of the sub queries. This BlendedTermQuery.RewriteMethod is useful when having a good match on a single field is considered better than having average matches on several fields.

    • Constructor Summary

      BlendedTermQuery.DisjunctionMaxRewrite(float tieBreakerMultiplier)
      This BlendedTermQuery.RewriteMethod will create DisjunctionMaxQuery instances that have the provided tie breaker.
